r, it is completely automated as it does not rest upon\nany manual labelling (either based on the users' features or on their sharing\npatterns). These elements make our method applicable to any Twitter discussion\nregardless of the language or the topic addressed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2020 09:19:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2021 09:16:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 2021 17:17:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 24 Jun 2021 11:13:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-29"}
